{"title":"海上炊事班","authors":["任海鹰"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":4,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上炊事班"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海军副观通长　任海鹰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管它狂风怒吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管它浪大滔天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来，小高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——做饭！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长张海山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"划根火柴把灶火点；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然一个大浪扑进来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈，火上加“油”，干！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长挺起胸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小高擦把“汗”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勺子、铲子掌在手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓与风浪夺午餐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打狼要有枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斩妖靠利剑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水兵与“敌”相争斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪能不吃饭？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快！炒熟菜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快！蒸上饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两人象跨上烈马背，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“翻山越岭”不下鞍……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“哇！”小高吐了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是黄水一片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他挤挤眼抬起头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唇边伸来水一碗……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长问他苦不苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他胸脯一拍：我是共青团员！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长紧握小高的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两颗红心一线牵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮位传来打靶捷报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战舰高歌猛向前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伙房里奏着“敲打乐”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪尖上飘着缕缕炊烟……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}